profile.profileDescription: A custom profile for a film archive

label.name_singular: Chicago Film Archives 329 West 18th Street, Chicago, IL 60616
label.name_plural: Chicago Film Archives 329 West 18th Street, Chicago, IL 60616

label.name: Library of Congress Subject Headings
label.description: Library of Congress Subject headings describing this object. To add a new heading simply type the first few letters of the heading and choose the desired one from the displayed list of possible matches.

label.name: GeoNames
label.description: A Geographic lookup that takes search text, passes it to the GeoNames search service and provides a dropdown with search results (ordered by score). Selected geoname is stored as both text (name, country, continent and ID) and the service URL identifier.

label.name: Language
label.description: The descriptor language identifies the primary language of a media item's audio or text. Alternative audio or text tracks and their associated languages should be identified using the descriptor alternativeModes.

label.name: Caption
label.description: Short descriptive caption for item.

label.name: Biography
label.description: Narrative biography for entity. This is the primary text used to document the entity.

label.name: Source of biography
label.description: Source of entity biography. This should be a formal citation if possible. For informal sources a narrative description is acceptable.

label.name: Institution
label.description: Name of the institution to which the collection belongs.

label.name: Abstract
label.description: Limited to one paragraph

label.name: Owner
label.description: Owning institution for collected materials

label.name: Status
label.description: Status of collection/finding aid processing

label.name: Loan Period (if owner is not CFA)
label.description: ONLY PROVIDE LOAN PERIOD INFORMATION IF OWNER IS NOT CFA

label.name: Repository
label.description: The institution or agency responsible for providing intellectual access to the materials being described

label.name: Access Restrictions
label.description: Information about conditions that affect availability of the collection as a whole or in part. May indicate need for an appointment or the nature of restrictions imposed by the donor, legal statute, etc.

label.name: Extent of collection
label.description: Summary of collection content.

label.name: Use Restrictions
label.description: Information about conditions that affect use of the collection as a whole or in part after access has been granted- what can a user do with the collected materials? Eg. Restrictions on reproduction due to copyright.

label.name: Accruals
label.description: Information about anticipated additions to the materials being described.

label.name: Organization and Arrangement
label.description: Information on how described materials have been subdivided into smaller units, identifying the logical or physical groupings within a hierarchical structure. This may include both ORGANIZATION and ARRANGEMENT as described by DACS.

label.name: Intellectual organization and arrangement
label.description: Information on how described materials have been subdivided into conceptual units.

label.name: Language of Finding Aid
label.description: Language the finding aid was written in.

label.name: Language of Materials
label.description: Languages represented by materials

label.name: Inventory Author
label.description: Name of individual responsible for compiling the intellectual content of the finding aid. NOTE that this field applies to the description of the ENTIRE collection, not inventorying of individual items.

label.name: Related Materials
label.description: Materials from other seriess related to those in series being described. Eg. Cover same topic, share creators, etc.

label.name: Separated Materials
label.description: Materials removed from series being described, including amount removed and reason for removal.

label.name: Length
label.description: Length of object

label.name: Width
label.description: Width of object

label.name: Height
label.description: Height of object

label.name: Depth
label.description: Depth of object

label.name: Thickness
label.description: Thickness of object

label.name: Repairs Made During Inspection
label.description: Repairs Made During Inspection

label.name: Georeference
label.description: Coordinates documenting the location of the item
